Package com.appdynamics.iot.events Description

Different types of events that can be instrumented

  • Events to report performance data for HTTP network requests NetworkRequestEvent
  • Events to report error and exception events ErrorEvent
  • Events to report any business specific custom event CustomEvent
The Instrumentation class provides static methods to collect and send these events.
